    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """LEARNING OUTCOMES (RD 822/2021)
The course contributes specifically to the following learning outcomes (competences, knowledge and abilities):
CG6, CG7, CG8, CG9, CE12.2, CE15, CE24, H.13, H.14, H.16
CE3 and CE4 are learning outcomes of the matter "Sustainability and Design," which this course belongs to. They appear linked with the course in the syllabus due to informatics limitations, but they are not RA of this course.
SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT GOALS
The course holds relathionship with the following SDG:
SDG 9: Industry, innovation and infrastructure.
SDG 12: Responsible cosumption and production."""@es ;
